Democratic forces may have "lost" in the Philippines last #Halalan2022, but we've seen the potential of the Millennials and Gen Zs.

Despite the pandemic, thousands, if not millions, came out to register.

Pink rallies were dominated by the youth.

Kabataan won with 500K votes.
